These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, onion, zucchini, eggplant
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil, tulip, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, epic, thriller
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic, fisherman, photographer
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person eating lemon is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
 6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
 8. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
10. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the scientist and the person eating lemon##7
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
12. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
13. the photographer is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | eggplant    | onion | zucchini    | lemon   |
| Flower   | marigold | tulip | daffodil | aconite |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery       | epic   | thriller  | zombie     |
| Job     | scientist      | fisherman   | photographer    | paramedic    |

