.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, reading, card-games
City: edinburgh, new-york, berlin, rome
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, brown, grey, lavender
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, sprite, iced-tea
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 2. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
 3. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes black##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 6. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who likes black##7
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
10. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
11. the person who likes brown is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | board-games   | reading       | card-games    | traveling      |
| City   | edinburgh | rome | new-york         | berlin   |
| Color   | lavender   | black  | brown       | grey |
| Beverage         | juice      | sprite  | iced-tea | milk |

