The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, swimming, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 3. the person eating pepper is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 7. the person eating blueberry is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person eating pumpkin##6
 9. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking water##1
11. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
12. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Food           | pumpkin | potato | pepper | blueberry |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate        | water    | mirinda    | almond-milk    |
| Birthday   | may        | march   | january   | august         |
| Sport           | soccer          | weightlifting       | skateboarding   | swimming           |

