 5. the havana-smoker is not the owner of the hamster##6
 6. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fan d&b##1
 8. the fan techno is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the havana-smoker##7
 9. the fan techno is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the colonial house is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the fan blues is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| House      | tower | colonial       | art-deco         | palace       |
