 9. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Game         | mah-jongg      | poker   | whist   | go       |
| Flower   | zinnia | begonia    | bellflower | daisy       |
| Transport   | boat  | airplane | motorbike   | bike     |
| House         | palace   | ranch-style    | gothic-revival   | townhouse |

