.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, bus, car
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, horror, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, vegafina, fonseca, chaman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, milk, hot-chocolate
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the fonseca-smoker is between the person driving the car and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 5. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person driving the airplane##7
 7. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
12. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport   | car      | bus     | snowmobile   | airplane    |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller | horror   | drama | crime |
| Cigar     | chaman        | fonseca     | bolivar  | vegafina      |
| Beverage   | tea       | hot-chocolate | soy-milk   | milk    |

 